getStatus

public String getStatus()
Gets the dial status of the fax.

Returns:
The dial status of the fax. Possible values for Outgoing fax are:
  • answered
  • unanswered
  • ongoing
  • failed
  • busy
Possible values for Incoming fax are:
  • ongoing
  • answered
  • failed
